dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Jack Allen. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Patricia Rogers.
Nice to meet you, Patricia. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is 5 8 2 1 0 9 and my date of birth is April ninth, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you, Patricia. One more thing, could you confirm your current address and primary contact number on file with us?
Of course. My address is 1 2 3 Main Street, Anytown, USA and my contact number is 5 5 5 5 1 2 3.
Thank you for providing the information, Patricia. Is there anything specific I can assist you with today regarding your policy or any other inquiries?
I wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, year, and VIN of the vehicle you wish to add.
Thank you for your time, Patricia. If you have any more questions or need further assistance in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
